reviewText: it was good....have all the others
This Nunsense movie is so funny. I went and bought the entire series.  If you are Catholic and suggest using a pair of Depends. It is that funny.
My wife loves the Nunsense videos. It's amusing to watch once (my opinion), she never tires of it. If you like Nunsense, I guess ya gotta add this one to your collection.
I will look for this vendor again.  The entire process was silky-smooth.  I saved a lot of money, and am very pleased.

I have all the other Nunsense dvds and I just had to add this one to my collection.
The movie is great, and I have already recommended it several people.
The DVD of the professional show helped give me ideas as I directed this musical comedy at our community theatre.
Saw the show in Macon GA earlier this year and bought it to remind myself of what a great time I had. I recommend seeing it in person if possible but loved reliving the memories with the DVD!
